channel.title: Tritanopia - By Ekstrak (My first song with Sound Packs!)
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/shane-brown-97094682/tritanopia
There is a trend where people are posting their songs for feedback, so I decided to do the same thing. I just brought 5 sound packs and I used them all at this one song. I really hope that people would like this trak. And if you do, thanks! ᵔ‿ᵔ
